text: Stanislav Dubrovsky (born 5 July 1974) is a Russian skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1994 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Russia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1994 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint Petersburg
